name.ja: アンドレアス (北風の王狼)

description.en: The Wolf of the North. A noble soul that watches over Wolvendom. It is said that its powers were given to it by an ancient god. Drops random Character Level-Up Materials, Artifacts, and Weapon Prototypes.
description.ru: Волк Севера. Можно сразиться раз в неделю для получения специальных наград.
